{"tid":1863352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"RTHK消息：再多兩人初步對新型肺炎測試呈陽性反應","createTime":"2020-02-05T06:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T07:09:28.000Z","uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2fc99d3eb1e702cd724d9e635748c67b4ae53b26","tid":1863352,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506770-20200205.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506770-20200205.htm&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcYGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=53e36ced\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506770-20200205.htm&h=7feb6412\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506770-20200205.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2020-02-05 HKT 14:00<br />\n分享工具 facebook twitter<br />\n消息指，一名60歲確診新型肺炎的男子，他的妻子和女兒，亦初步對新冠狀病毒測試呈陽性反應，結果有待進一步化驗確定。<br />\n<br />\n該名60歲確診男子者有長期病患，居在藍田康田苑裕康閣。他於1月22日出現發燒及肌肉痛，自1月30日出現呼吸困難，同日先到基督教聯合醫院求醫，其後到將軍澳醫院求診併入院接受治療。病人在病發期間，亦曾先後向4名私家醫生求醫，潛伏期內沒有外遊，主要逗留在家中。他的妻子及女兒正在聯合醫院接受治療。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50ed76ffecb49fbd3593ea926cb5c655f568cef","tid":1863352,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:05:55.000Z","msg":"確診埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef9640f7a3e0186ab5a3232e331fb16f2df9684","tid":1863352,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"19同20單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675cbf061cef640fdc57ae97a932340ebae62b54","tid":1863352,"uid":290838,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-